  "### 5.2 Parallel Trends",
  "",
  "Over the twenty-month pre-groundbreaking window (January 2020 through August 2021), impact-zone and control-zone tracts appreciated at 2.1 percent and 2.4 percent annualized, respectively. The Wald-test *p*-value on the difference is 0.31; the event-study leads (Figure A1) are jointly indistinguishable from zero at the 5 percent level. The parallel-trends assumption is not directly testable, but the pre-period data are consistent with it.",
