  "### 5.5 Spatial Heterogeneity Within the Ring",
  "",
  "The six-year cumulative appreciation rate varies substantially across the eleven impact-zone tracts. The four tracts with the highest rates concentrate in the northwestern sector of the ring, directly adjacent to the Center's 62nd Street entrance:",
  "",
